code: [' function execute_command(image){const e=new ImagePatch(image);const t=e.find("person");const n=e.find("tennis racket");const r=n[0].right;const i=t.filter(p=>p.left>r);return i.length>0?bool_to_yesno(i[0].exists("hat")):"no"}']
query: Is the person to the right of the tennis racket wearing a hat?

code: [' function execute_command(image){const e=new ImagePatch(image);const t=e.find("lamp");const n=t[0].llm_query("What is in front of the lamp?",!1);return n}']

code: [' function execute_command(image){const e=new ImagePatch(image);const t=e.find("jacket");const n=t[0];const r=n.verify_property("jacket","dark");const i=n.verify_property("jacket","long sleeved");return bool_to_yesno(r&&i)}']

code: [' function execute_command(image){const imagePatch=new ImagePatch(image);const lampPatches=imagePatch.find("lamp");const lampPatch=lampPatches[0];const buildingPatches=imagePatch.find("building");const buildingPatch=buildingPatches[0];const lampToBuildingDistance=distance(lampPatch,buildingPatch);const lampToBuildingAngle=Math.atan2(lampToBuildingDistance,imagePatch.computeDepth());const lampToBuildingDirection=lampToBuildingAngle*180/Math.PI;return imagePatch.llmQuery(`What is in front of the lamp that is ${lampToBuildingDirection} of the building?`,!1)}']
query: What is in front of the lamp that is in front of the building?
